params.markdown:
**Overview**

The Agents Dashboard provides a detailed overview of all agents and their current state within the environment. Pie charts display various distributions, including active agent status, firewall status, scan status, group IP, OS architecture, machine type, OS name and type, infected agents status, up-to-date status, pending uninstall status, and application vulnerability status. It also highlights the percentage of uninstalled agents for tracking overall deployment health. Bar charts present insights into agents by mitigation mode, installer type, and computer names with active threats, helping to identify areas that require attention. Additionally, a table lists the top 10 site names, offering a quick view of locations with the most agent activity. This dashboard enables effective monitoring, threat detection, and overall agent management.
